name: Blackwing Descent
text: Special Summon 1 Level 3 or lower "Blackwing" monster from your hand or Deck, its effect(s) are negated, but banish it during the End Phase of this turn. You cannot Summon/Set other monsters except "Blackwing" monsters or "Black-Winged Dragon" the turn you activate this card. (This includes even before you activate this card.)
